set nocompatible
set number
set relativenumber

autocmd Filetype gitcommit setlocal spell textwidth=72

filetype on
filetype plugin on
filetype indent on
syntax on

" Disable Arrow keys
map <up> <nop>
map <down> <nop>
map <left> <nop>
map <right> <nop>
imap <up> <nop>
imap <down> <nop>
imap <left> <nop>
imap <right> <nop>
